	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會演奏<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />？<delay frames="30" />
